<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lift-v">lift <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /lɪft/    美 /lɪft/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi (被) 举起；(被) 抬起：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He lifted his glass to the health of his parents. 
他举杯祝父母身体健康。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The student <strong>lifted his hand</strong> to signal the teacher that he knew the answer. 
那个学生举起手示意老师他知道答案。</p></div>

<h4 id="2vi-vt">2.<strong>vi &amp; vt (使) 提高；(使) 高涨；(使) 振奋：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Watching a comedy can help to <strong>lift your spirits</strong>.
看喜剧有助你开心起来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His heart lifted at the sight of her. 
他一看见她就高兴了起来。</p></div>

<h4 id="3vi">3.<strong>vi (云、雾等) 消散：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The fog began to lift. 
雾开始消散。</p></div></div>